{"tid":1590091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"( 建國請廣傳 ) 我要國歌嘅symphony譜！！！我要人人一支黑紫荊旗","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:40:09.000Z","uid":250365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a606bb0c82690913b729409afb93bdfb2186ad81","tid":1590091,"uid":250365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"如題，有冇人有願榮光歸香港嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">管弦學譜</span></span>，求share！<br />\n<br />\n依家各大商場差唔多每日都有人嗌口號唱國歌，有必要有份分每個樂器聲部嘅symphony譜，廣傳出去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建國</span>呢啲講緊嘅係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歸屬感</span>同一啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">標誌性嘅嘢</span>，例如黑紫荊國旗同國歌等，必須令呢啲嘢普及於市民。其實大家要多啲舉黑紫荊旗，rather than美國英國旗，一黎我地必須建立一啲屬於香港人嘅嘢，二黎喺前線有旗更加可以振奮士氣！<br />\n<br />\n所以希望有本地音樂人可以執一set symphony譜同總譜出黎，等大家無論玩咩樂器都可以練熟自己嗰part！唔該香港人！"},{"pid":"aafa8aa9782d28e4bc9573d3e785a2c365671b53","tid":1590091,"uid":250365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:29:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"472af1a7a13407791561ac23843bae352808dcbb","tid":1590091,"uid":250365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aacb1e74fb7fa376b5433c4655cba6991507b5a4","tid":1590091,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"4768466d0f55a50ad3fc2f229c436995bcf68a8f","tid":1590091,"uid":250365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e49d8585b3ea29870026e685a973859ad223344e","tid":1590091,"uid":250365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T